'Bertemu dia.
Dia adalah tunangan saya.'

00:21:50.200 --> 00:21:52.080 line:20%
'Garv, dia yang..
- Hai, Ishani.'

00:21:53.120 --> 00:21:55.320 line:20%
'Kalian saling kenal?  - Ya.'

